                            <comment id="253958" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2019 18:27:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Talking to Behlendorf he suspects its the addition of project quotas to ZFS for the 0.8.1 version. The additional space consumed is included with their stats.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
